title: Element Soul Adventure - Fall 2015
description:
After introducing the Element Fall 2015 Soul Adventure collection, Part 1 earlier this season - where the journey started in the heart of San Francisco, the Northern California skateboarding mecca - the Soul Adventure Part 2 will see the journey continue south alongside the Highway 1 coastline to finish in Big Sur. 
Follow the Element team riders who endure the coastal and mountain terrain and end up making a surprise discovery.
